Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:59.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:04.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:11.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:16.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:21.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:30.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:35.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:38.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:43.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:47.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:50.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:55.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:02.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:59.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜歡著緊張的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:04.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}興奮起來走向更廣闊的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:11.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:16.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只專注於眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:21.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰都無法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前進的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}連同那份淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:30.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部開始閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:35.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此將宿於手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:38.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}盡情揮揚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果斷地  徑直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:43.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向著明天全力進發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:47.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在轉瞬即逝之間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:50.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}實現那夢中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}無論它多麼虛幻和遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:55.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也絕不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和僅屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:02.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹劍節奏響徹永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:15.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第15話\N初次合宿與初次去澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯我放在冰箱裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得用微波爐熱一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天傍晚我就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  今晚住學校是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能…回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就不是合宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的時候不要碰我的DVD錄像機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能碰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  比你要厲害就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手下那幫人都說想和川添珠姬再打一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家小珠在那之後可是又變強了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為打工的緣故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別承認得那麼爽快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  怎麼啦  出了車站迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  因為明美中途想要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫尾去追的時候撞上了自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混亂的小西又差點昏過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她恢復結果就遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你跑得不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…今天人家有事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是男人吧  給我分手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道和男人就像魚和熊掌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從橫尾嘴裡說出來很有說服力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之大家來打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的合宿打攪您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我要去男生那邊看看所以先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我再過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…大家已經在道場等我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳池？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那裡好黏！噁心！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不瞭解勞動的樂趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這黏黏的感覺才正是打掃泳池最大的樂趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非要做這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少林寺！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮花君  我覺得這個離人遠點再玩比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃泳池？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟我們學校的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長家鄰居的那個老太婆稍微有些過節
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不作這種義工的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿許可根本不會給我批不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以抱歉了  在打掃結束前請你們等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道場隨你們用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那我們也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  人多打掃起來也快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省下的時間也能來練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:04:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  橫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動移動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼大家都無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不合情理嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得週末卻要打掃泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來今晚有約會的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚？晚上？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新交到的  要幫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊好像溢出什麼黑色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:05:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次雖然毫無還手之力來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這次會更努力一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正  多關照啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安藤  你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣戰佈告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和小珠你比過的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼名字來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  已經差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  放水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！快關上  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼罵我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先放輕鬆做下柔韌度鍛煉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當增進感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  平時不都是差不多就開始了嗎  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時是平時  今天是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來準備開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人一組出列
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據身材從對方學校選對手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吉川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  真的在合宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是兩天一夜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過給人感覺很熱血嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱血…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一回我再帶慰問品過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:07:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎老師和吉川老師是一對了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  完全看不出是那樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還遠遠不明白女人心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山手線…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  抬腳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央線…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像山洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:36.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（山手線和中央線都是日本兩個環狀鐵路線的名稱）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼  腳扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護具的味道消除不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護具的味道消除不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨季的霉菌都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨季的霉菌都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摺足和繼足還有送足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摺足和繼足還有送足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能拿竹劍打高爾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能拿竹劍打高爾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能拿竹劍去打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那麼說沒有三年生？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有  可是大家都在準備升學考試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原田你們不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我打算在夏季大會結束後再考慮考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拿到哪裡的推薦名額就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠他們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現在的練習方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是唱那歌有什麼意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町戶和室江是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町戶和室江是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我感覺什麼在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是貓呀狗呀狸貓之類啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是那樣啦  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嗎…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴頭盔！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼重來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我上  讓我上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你按順序來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閃開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩佐和外山去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭一次進行這樣的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有4個小時了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好好上了一課呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連一局都沒有贏過川添同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在我們部裡面也沒有人能從小珠那裡贏上一局哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連那個老師也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…還是不要說的那麼明白比較…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就只能賭在明天的練習賽上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,論綜合戰力我們還是有希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺川  這次你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我聽好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼嘛  大將
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在發簡訊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我給你刪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  過分！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師說吃晚飯之前大家先去澡堂洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師有給錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種久違的感覺呢  進澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有淋浴壞了才會來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像從一年級之後就沒來過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在裡面游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進澡堂囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始戰鬥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日文裡{\fe128\fscx85\fscy96\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}銭湯{\r}和{\fe128\fscx85\fscy96\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}戦闘{\r}同音，但這裡東貌似不是有意說冷笑話的樣子…）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡就是舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次來澡堂有什麼感想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂好大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到合宿當然就是咖喱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天拜託阿姨做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要吃完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後點心就是吉川老師的慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備了一些冰棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰棒放在冰箱裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人一個大家自己去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  開始用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有味噌汁嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添同學把咖喱和味噌汁放在一起吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過前幾天我搞錯把砂糖放進味噌汁裡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個和這個完全沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶慰問品來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥？前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  是壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是壽司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極品的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱和壽司一起吃如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人的學校給人感覺就是興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫尾同學你的反應好像動物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是貓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老貓？還是小貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫什麼喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？町戶的人是不是少了一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來明美呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟我說要去下廁所…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會連各位的份也一起歡樂度過的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼東西啊  這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是打算逃走結果摔倒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那剛剛的慘叫聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說應該是摔倒的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西山  把這傢伙背回去讓她睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來比剛入學的時候要快樂許多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入劍道部沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天也有這種感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來也還算滿快樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃  氣合！氣合！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2  氣合啊  紀梨乃加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃！紀梨乃！加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣合啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫尾  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟死人一樣  聲音大一點啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩！加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫尾同學  能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:16:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江校勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種比賽也贏不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  川添同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了大伙  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我為了今天為了兩校的劍道部創作了一首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望大家一定要聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  小鞘唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲名是「Respect my friend forever with true love」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請大家欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來扔枕頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到合宿  就是要扔枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫尾同學  那是休學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！這樣的話不管搞什麼我一定要贏室江一次  看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要朝我這扔…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子不要命了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是扔枕頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  你這樣豈不是很沒意思嘛  快來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:22.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（畫像上的偉人們表情都很微妙啊…）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼東西在亂飛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要睡這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  這就是所謂的「紳士精神」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  趕快睡覺睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我關燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這麼快就睡著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺睡不著嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為第一次合宿所以很興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想去年現在簡直跟騙人的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能這麼有幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都多虧了小珠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是因為小珠加入  才使劍道部發生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想現在才能這麼快樂的去努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…就算是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別拿我開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:43.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超劍戰隊  Blade Braver ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥英雄系列30週年紀念  特別節目！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:56.68,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待てよ！　邪悪な牙を剥いて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:21:02.78,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗤う　悪のデスアーマー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:08.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺が！　俺たちが許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:14.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危険上等　ブレイブチェンジ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:24.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}超剣戦隊ブレードブレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:56.68,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}住手吧！  剝下邪惡的爪牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:21:02.78,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}嗤笑著  邪惡的Death Armour
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:08.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我不能！  我們不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:14.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}危險最高  Brave Change!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:24.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}{\fad(0,500)}超劍戰隊 Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾諸位了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  這次練習非常有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大會預選賽  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  你們也加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？合宿的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不開燈啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小夜風濡れた髪を 指にからませ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}解けない 謎ときに ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前は 澄み渡った 星空なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心には 切ない雲 たちこめたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私を  照らす星が あるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ小さな  光でもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}いくつも チャンスたちが 待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}いつの日にか 見つけるわ 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}將被夜風潤濕的頭髮  纏在手指上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}獨自解開那難解的謎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮現出晴朗的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心中仍被苦惱的烏雲所籠罩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一定存在照耀著我的那顆星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}雖然還很渺小  但有光芒就已足夠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}很多次機會在等待著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}終有一日  定會找到那顆流星…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.59,0:23:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為交給這兩個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果世界征服的計劃一點都沒有進展
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.85,0:24:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我有」「我治」「我享」的理想國家安藤樂園\N還沒建好節目就要完結了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後就讓我親自出馬來解決Braver那個傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.28,0:24:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個歸那個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集要放的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「紀梨乃的缺席與預選大會」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集還請大家繼續…看不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:18.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這最後一句總感覺在EG那個神級作品「Excel Sage」）
